作家鲍勃·盖尔（Bob Gale）说，“回到未来4”将永远不会发生https://www.nme.com/news/film/back-to-the-future-4-will-never-happen-says-writer-bob-gale-3835557?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=back-to- Future-4-Will-norver-Happen-Says Worter-Bob-GaleVictoria Luxford Thu, 06 Feb 2025 14:16:06 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3835557 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="回到未来" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>任何要求都有钝器的响应</p><p>作家鲍勃·盖尔<a href="https://www.nme.com">（</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/back-to-the-future-4-will-never-happen-says-writer-bob-gale-3835557">Bob Gale）说，“回到未来4”的帖子将永远不会发生</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="回到未来" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Back-To-The-Future-Film-Still-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont