complex.com/music/a/markelibert/drake-denies-dj-khaled-claim-two-songs-new-album-drake-bell" target="_blank" rel="noopener">复杂</a></em>）中出场。最近的两个贡献包括歌曲“ Khaled Khaled”和“上帝做到了”。</p><p>在宣布“热线布林”说唱歌手将与另一位艺术家合作创作新专辑的几天后，就会解雇另一种伙伴关系。据报道，周一（2月3日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-and-partynextdoor-announce-joint-album-exy-ongs-4-u-3834255">，他和PartyNextdoor将于下周发布名为“ $ Exy $ ongs 4 U”的LP</a> 。</p><p>这一消息是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-performs-toronto-themed-cover-of-hey-there-delilah-announces-new-album-with-partynextdoor-3780758">德雷克（Drake）去年夏天在多伦多（Toronto）演出期间提到</a>的。 “代表我和聚会，我们一直在为大家做些事情，”他在活动中告诉球迷。</p><p> “当有点冷时，[PartyNextdoor和Drake专辑都会在那里等待。” </p><figure id="attachment_3826013" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3826013" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3826013" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Drake.-CREDIT_-Mark-Blinch_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Drake.-CREDIT_-Mark-Blinch_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Drake.-CREDIT_-Mark-Blinch_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Drake.-CREDIT_-Mark-Blinch_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Drake.-CREDIT_-Mark-Blinch_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Drake.-CREDIT_-Mark-Blinch_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Drake.-CREDIT_-Mark-Blinch_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3826013" class="wp-caption-text">德雷克。学分：马克·布林奇/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>该唱片将是Drake自2023年以来的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/drake-for-all-the-dogs-review-tracklist-lyrics-3511670">所有狗</a>”以来的第一个，该唱片是<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/drake-for