/artists/slash">Slash</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/GUNS-N-ROSES">Guns N&#39;Roses</a>的<a href="/artists/duff-mckagan">Duff McKagan</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alice-in-chains">《爱丽丝》中的爱丽丝</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/limp-bizkit">li行Bizkit</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/KORN">Korn</a>的成员，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rage-against-the-machine">对机器</a>的汤姆·莫雷洛（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">Tom Morello）</a>的愤怒（他也是音乐会音乐总监的表演）。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ozzy-osbourne-tour-retirement-black-sabbath-3390656"><b>Ozzy Osbourne：摇滚乐表演者与众不同</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这是一个挤满了法案，向这一类型的先驱说再见，但是，在Villa Park宣布<em>这一</em>消息后不久，Sharon表示，乐队的遗产太深刻了，无法真正消失。 </p><figure id="attachment_3835047" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3835047" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3835047" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-sabbath-poster@2000x1270.jpg" alt="黑色安息日“回到开始”海报" width="2000" height="2818" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-sabbath-poster@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-sabbath-poster@2000x1270-400x564.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-sabbath-poster@2000x1270-800x1127.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-sabbath-poster@2000x1270-696x981.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-sabbath-poster@2000x1270-1392x1961.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-sabbath-poster@2000x1270-1068x1505.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3835047" class="wp-caption-text">黑色安息日“回到开始”海报。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>“你不能说再见，”奥兹的妻子和经理告诉<em>NME</em> 。 “看看他们留下的东西 - 这是他们留给世界的巨大，伟大的工作。只要您有的话，它就永远不会再见。它是为了永恒的。”</p><p>她承认，丈夫Ozzy目前对最后一场表演感到“非常激动”，这是“他想要的”。</p><p> “他想对所有人表示感谢。由于病的病，他没有机会，但是现在他确实有机会。”</p><p> Iommi感谢所有同意表演并向安息日致敬的乐队，然后Osbourne补充说：“您能想象所有这些家伙在一起的照片吗？这里有一大堆图标。那张结局的照片将是不可思议的，历史上将倒下。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFu3ZyBzEea/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,4