athan [Davis]将会在这里，他可能会和[ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/RED-HOT-CHILLI-PEPPERS">Red Hot Chili Peppers</a> &#39;] Chad Smith或任何人一起玩！爱丽丝的链条即将到来，他们正在作为乐队演奏。” </p><figure id="attachment_3835543" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3835543" style="width: 1333px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3835543" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_2.jpg" alt="沙龙·奥斯本（Sharon Osbourne）参加了黑安息日在维拉公园（Villa Park）的最后节目“回到开始”（萨米尔·侯赛因（Samir Hussein）/盖蒂（Getty Images）" width="1333" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_2.jpg 1333w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_2-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_2-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_2-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_2-1068x1602.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1333px) 100vw, 1333px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3835543" class="wp-caption-text">沙龙·奥斯本（Sharon Osbourne）参加了黑安息日在别墅公园（Villa Park）宣布的最后一场节目“回到一开始”（萨米尔·侯赛因（Samir Hussein）/盖蒂（Getty Images）/盖蒂（Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p><strong>哇。您不喜欢仅仅是安息日和一些支持乐队的更简单的任务吗？</strong></p><p><strong>奥斯本（Osbourne）：</strong> “不，这是一个庆祝活动 - 启动并将其传递给所有这些乐队的流派和先驱者。通常，当您死了时，这件事就完成了 - 因此，这些家伙能够被感激！”</p><p> <strong>iommi：</strong> “我只是在想！我们现在就拥有它。”</p><p><strong>托尼，您会全天与其他任何人一起打扰吗？</strong></p><p> <strong>iommi：</strong> “不，我会和我的乐队一起拥挤。”</p><p><strong>很公平！您最期待看到谁？</strong></p><p><strong>奥斯本：</strong> “你所有的老伴侣？”</p><p> <strong>Iommi：</strong> “这将是与所有人一起参加的事件。我不会整天站在那儿，这是肯定的。他们全都在我们身边，真是太好了。”</p><p><strong>奥斯本：</strong> “我们甚至有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-black">杰克·布莱克</a>。他正在新西兰拍摄，所以他无法做到，但是他正在与儿子和汤姆·莫雷洛（Tom Morello）的儿子和其他一些孩子在<em>摇滚学校</em>一起制作视频。看到人们的孩子受到安息日的影响，这真是太神奇了。我们53年后我们在这里，这一世代已经消失了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3823477" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823477" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823477" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Black-Sabbath-posing-1.jpg" alt="麦迪逊广场花园的黑色安息日照片，托尼·艾姆米（Tony Iommi）和奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Black-Sabbath-posing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Black-Sabbath-posing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Black-Sabbath-posing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Black-Sabbath-posing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Black-Sabbath-posing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Black-Sabbath-posing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3823477" class="wp-caption-text"> Black Sabbath的Tony Iommi和Ozzy Osbourne在舞台上进行现场表演（Fin Costello/Redferns照片）</figcaption></figure><p> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/download-festival-boss-2025-lineup-pressures-sleep-token-3812318">关于旧乐队的新行为逐步下载了新的行为，</a>已经有很多讨论。您如何看待当前的岩石和金属乐队浪潮？</strong></p><p><strong>奥斯本（Osbourne）：</strong> “好吧，科恩（Korn）是一支传统乐队 - 我们与他们合作已有25年了。时间是这样的；不受干扰的。那太棒了。人们没有意识到的是，像科恩， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/judas-priest">[犹大]牧师</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/acdc">AC/DC</a>和安息日这样的乐队比以往任何时候都大。音乐行业总是在周期中进行，并且又一次转动。人们希望看到真正的音乐家正在用乐器播放自己的歌曲，而不是从卧室的计算机上完成。吉他再次赞赏。</p><p>这些乐队经受了时间的考验。看安息日：57年前做出的事情如何仍然像今天这样销售和声音？有某些专辑和艺术家经受了时间的考验，听起来并没有过时。”</p><p> <strong>iommi</strong> ：“这真是不可思议 - 我们如何接受时间的考验。当您回想起我们制作第一张专辑的时间时，我们会在两天内生活。能够知道我们这样做真是太好了。那些日子很棒。”</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ozzy-osbourne-tour-retirement-black-sabbath-3390656"><b>Ozzy Osbourne：摇滚乐表演者与众不同</b></a></strong></li></ul><p><strong>目前Ozzy怎么样？</strong></p><p><strong>奥斯本：</strong> “他真的很棒。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-says-living-with-parkinsons-disease-makes-him-feel-like-hes-walking-around-in-lead-boots-3301202">他有帕金森氏症</a>，我们都知道，但他很棒，这不会影响他的声音。”</p><p> <strong>iommi：</strong> “这将对他很好，做这个节目。真的会的。这就是全部：他想出去做某事。”</p><p><strong>奥斯本：</strong> “他觉得自己从来没有机会感谢粉丝。说“谢谢您的这种令人难以置信的生活”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3835544" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3835544" style="width: 1333px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3835544" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_3.jpg" alt="Tony Iommi参加了Villa Park的Black Sabbath的最后一场节目“ Back To Kithing”的宣布（Samir Hussein的照片/Getty Images for Live Nation UK）" width="1333" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_3.jpg 1333w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_3-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_3-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_3-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_3-1068x1602.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1333px) 100vw, 1333px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3835544" class="wp-caption-text"> Tony Iommi参加了Black Sabbath在Villa Park举行的Black Sabbath的最后一场节目“ Back To Kithing”的宣布（Samir Hussein的照片/Getty Images for Live Nation UK）</figcaption></figure><p><strong>很高兴您也选择了这些慈善机构，因此不仅仅是发薪日。</strong></p><p> <strong>Iommi：</strong> “我以为我们要保留钱吗？”</p><p><strong>奥斯本：</strong> “停止它！”</p><p> <strong>Iommi：</strong> “不，这些确实是很棒的原因。”</p><p><strong>奥斯本（Osbourne）：</strong> “伯明翰（Birmingham）做了很多事情，并且是他们本人的重要组成部分。他们不是这些降低口音并突然成为摇滚明星的乐队之一。安息日一直是伯明翰出生的。这是金属的家，这是它开始的地方。奥兹（Ozzy）的父亲在金属工厂工作，实际上是在制造金属！”</p><p> <strong>Iommi：</strong> “他为我们制作了这些铝十字架，这就是我们开始的。”</p><p><strong>奥斯本：</strong> “这都是有机的，纯净的，从未人为。回来说谢谢这意味着很多，因为那是他们的身份。他们是有梦想的普通人，梦想成真。要在您的生活中处于某种位置，然后将其归还给城市，“因为您使我成为我。”</p><p> <strong>Iommi：</strong> “他们真的为我们感到骄傲，伯明翰现在。当然，在早期，他们并不知道我们不知道我们的意思，但是现在他们对我们说的话还不够。桌子已经转过身。”</p><p><strong>奥斯本：</strong> “他们刚刚被授予城市自由。”</p><p><strong>这允许您做什么？</strong></p><p><strong>奥斯本：</strong> “他们可以做任何他们想做的！”</p><p><strong>可能会有一些新的材料掉落或及时的演出单曲，还是只是说再见？</strong></p><p><strong>奥斯本（Osbourne）：</strong> “这只是庆祝仍然生活的旧音乐。您进入职业生涯的舞台，无论您做什么都不能忍受您以前所做的事情。为了能够休息并留下来，“人们仍然喜欢它，它仍然在卖出，我们不能比我们所做的事情更好”，这足够了。”</p><p> <strong>iommi：</strong> “这些专辑所做的事情真是太神奇了。”</p><p><strong>奥斯本（Osbourne）：</strong> “我总是对人说，&#39;这不是同一个人购买唱片的另一副本 - 这是新一代。您正在教育新人有关这项工作的知识。这是关于庆祝的。有时，当人们随着年龄的增长而继续创作新音乐时，这并不能忍受他们以前所做的事情。我永远不想看到它们不到第一。” </p><figure id="attachment_3835545" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3835545" style="width: 1333px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3835545" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_4.jpg" alt="Tony Iommi和Sharon Osbourne参加了Villa Park的Black Sabbath的最后一个节目“ Back to the Start”的宣布（Samir Hussein的照片/Getty Images for Live Nation UK）" width="1333" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_4.jpg 1333w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_4-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_4-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_4-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabbath_villa_4-1068x1602.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1333px) 100vw, 1333px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3835545" class="wp-caption-text"> Tony Iommi和Sharon Osbourne参加了Villa Park的Black Sabbath的最后一场节目“ Back To to to the Stain”的宣布（Samir Hussein的照片/Getty Images for Live Nation UK）</figcaption></figure><p><strong>好莱坞是否一直在打电话制作安息日传记片并结束故事？</strong></p><p> <strong>iommi：</strong> “谁知道？我们从没想过会发生<em>这种情况</em>。”</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/the-big-read-ozzy-osbourne-interview-2612386#:~:text=The%20Big%20Read%20%E2%80%93%20Ozzy%20Osbourne%3A%20%E2%80%9C,This%20album%20saved%20my%20life%E2%80%9D&amp;text=%E2%80%9CI'm%20sitting%20in%20the,a%20house%20in%20Bel%20Air.">Ozzy Osbourne在封面上：“这张专辑挽救了我的生命”</a></strong></li></ul><p> <strong>Who would play you guys?</strong></p><p> <strong>Osbourne:</strong> “God only knows! If it were to happen, I don&#39;t know well-known actors would be good to do it. With these characters, you&#39;d need to get somebody new. You can get these phenomenal actors: if you got Johnny Depp playing Ozzy, all you&#39;d see in the movie is Johnny Depp. It has to be somebody faceless at that time.”</p><p> <strong>And as for life the show – what&#39;s happens then?</strong></p><p> <strong>Iommi:</strong> “Who knows?”</p><p> <strong>Osbourne</strong> : “Exactly. They&#39;ve achieved and done so much. Now it&#39;s their time to just do their thing.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Black Sabbath - interview with Ozzy Osbourne, Tony Iommi and Geezer Butler" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ODq02WXMY3o?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Black Sabbath&#39;s &#39;Back The The Beginning&#39; takes place at Birmingham&#39;s Villa Park on Saturday July 5. Tickets go on sale next Friday (February 14) at 10am GMT <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fblack-sabbath-tickets%2Fartist%2F734569" target="_blank" rel="noopener">and will be available here</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-interview-sharon-ozzy-osbourne-tony-iommi-health-birmingham-villa-park-final-show-new-material-3835523">Sharon Osbourne and Tony Iommi tell us about Black Sabbath&#39;s finale: “Usually this thing is done when you&#39;re dead”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 Outbreak 2025: Glassjaw to play classic albums in full as more names join line-up https://www.nme.com/news/music/outbreak-2025-glassjaw-to-play-classic-albums-in-full-as-more-names-join-line-up-3835553?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=outbreak-2025-glassjaw-to-play-classic-albums-in-full-as-more-names-join-line-upLiberty Dunworth Thu, 06 Feb 2025 12:34:06 +0000 Music NewsNewsHardcoreLive Music NewsPunkRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3835553 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Daryl Palumbo and Justin Beck of Glassjaw perform live" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Terror, Big Boy, XWEAPONX, Pest Control and Jivebomb are among the new additions</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/outbreak-2025-glassjaw-to-play-classic-albums-in-full-as-more-names-join-line-up-3835553">Outbreak 2025: Glassjaw to play classic albums in full as more names join line-up</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Daryl Palumbo and Justin Beck of Glassjaw perform live" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/glassjaw@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> New names have been added to the line-up for Outbreak 2025, including <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glassjaw">Glassjaw</a> who will break out some of their classic albums in full.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/outbreak-fest-2018-live-review-photos-2355853">Outbreak Fest&#39;s tenth edition was a visceral, thrilling celebration of the last true subculture</a></strong></li></ul><p> The <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/outbreak-2025-slowdive-knocked-loose-alex-g-danny-brown-for-stacked-manchester-festival-line-up-3816098">first wave of artists joining this year&#39;s instalment</a> of the festival was shared back in November, and it was confirmed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/knocked-loose">Knocked Loose</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alex-g">Alex G</a> would be leading the line-up.</p><p> For the former, the slot comes following their new album <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-knocked-loose-and-poppy-crushing-new-single-suffocate-3749930">&#39;You Won&#39;t Go Before You&#39;re Supposed To&#39;</a> , and other names joining the bill included Danny Brown, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-curry">Denzel Curry</a> , <a href="https://nme-next.netlify.app/artists/momma">Momma</a> , Tigers Jaw, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sunny-day-real-estate">Sunny Day Real Estate</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drug-church">Drug Church</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slowdive">Slowdive</a> and Superheaven, as well as former <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover"><em>NME</em> Cover stars</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/militarie-gun-03-07-2023-3463853">Militarie Gun</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/model-actriz-25-09-2023-3503348">Model/Actriz</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/julie-band-23-09-2024-3795997">Julie</a> .</p><p> This year&#39;s edition of Outbreak will also see a London date added to the mix – as well as the regular site at the BEC Arena in Manchester. The one-day stop in the capital will be held on June 13, while the Manchester instalment will be held on June 14 and 15.</p><p> Now, a host of new artists have been added to the line-up, including post-hardcore legends Glassjaw who will use the slots to break out some of their classic albums in full. For the Manchester sets, they&#39;ll perform a full run-through of &#39;Worship And Tribute&#39; on the 14th and &#39;Everything You Ever Wanted To Know About Silence&#39; on the 15th. The London show will see a blend of the two tracklists. </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFs7ucGNt65/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></di